methodology.single_station: If only one weather station was present within the county or territory boundary, then the cooling and heating design temperatures for that weather station were assigned to the entire county or territory.
methodology.multiple_stations: If more than one weather station was present within the county or territory boundary, then the highest cooling and lowest heating design temperatures among the weather stations in the county or territory were assigned to the entire county or territory.
methodology.no_stations: If no weather stations were present within the county boundary, then the cooling and heating design temperatures for the closest weather station were assigned to the entire county.
